"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640063031,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"0zHNiEG3Q35Sqt2ovDQHNq7P_KG0u4Z-_YocZM3_V1c\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x893Eba31647Aa6B2ed2A1EC6BC8900deEcdE4476\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"VWjp0ja3jSshV9JCsStWx8YzIVIemAoeFdX8ElTYlFk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"DjRGeEfr5P6FwBQpjcXnTNldwSMtP5mb9KUCVd_cSjk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"_hLWKfnE0hnLhcuMyt4go8sscFLp7E4TuBslX6xzTGqvTaSFYhqc4_68Q53_wo2tA_m7KuiydHh97dpQsCyM6g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe6c29c9a36678d9447bf446f65850857419bbf26f6b66ae306f35cd8d8cf283b405f1f4608c04a609351664bd889e95a808b942ade7f8bd37e7da6f89c60cb171b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"VWjp0ja3jSshV9JCsStWx8YzIVIemAoeFdX8ElTYlFk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"DjRGeEfr5P6FwBQpjcXnTNldwSMtP5mb9KUCVd_cSjk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi